      "content": "Stating the projections are completely stable or the confidence level is definitively high would be an overstatement based on the current data. The current volatility necessitates a more nuanced presentation to the Board. Instead, frame the volatility as inherent to early-stage compound evaluation but emphasize the *trajectory* of improvement as your core strength. This allows you to defend the investment by showing positive momentum despite data noise.",
